Description:
You arrive at the eastern farmlands with Betty intact when a farmer approaches you and says:

"Oooh you found Betty! thank you so much strangers, even being so small, she is my favorite sheep and I won several local contests with her, I wonder how she got away.

I don't have much gold... but you might be interested in hearing a rumor as to where the legendary golden sheep might be?"
DescriptionAction: What do you want as a reward?
